title: MetaStreet DAO Repurchase Agreement Durations
body:
This is a NEGATIVE CONSENT vote - if a quorum of greater than 20% is reached, the proposal will be deemed to be denied by the DAO. If no quorum is reached, the proposal will be deemed to be accepted by the DAO.
Proposal: MetaStreet DAO will participate in repurchase agreements on existing NFT collateral platforms (NFTFi and PawnFi, as examples). MetaStreet DAO will participate in 30, 60 and 90 day agreements.
author: 0xD1Affe275f09cD11bfDf38F3c9b85c016F47b75e
